measurements.description: Six flowers on six 0.5-cm inflorescences; sepals acuminate, burgundy, green tips and abaxial surface ; petals acuminate, porrect, burgundy, green tips and abaxial surface; lip cream, heavily overlaid burgundy blotches basal two-thirds, less on apical one-third; column light green overlaid burgundy, anther cap light green; substance impressively firm; texture matte; unusually long 5.0cm pedicel; fragrance light coconut, citrus component atypical, identity verified by SITF.
